channel.title: Can anyone help?
channel.description:
Im not sure if this is right section but here's my problem....
Im using Galkons Client base and tried adding models I added the ints and the model gziped or whatever into my models folder i went in game on that client and tried adding the model. It didn't work and as i saw in other pics it's a totally different thing in theirs... I know i am doing it right cause i followed a tut... Just for some reason it's not working I don't know if it's the client base or something so [b]if it is can someone post a link to a client or a client base?[/b] I need help quick! also the galkons has a lot of nulls so if anyone could help thanks very much!
As an example id go in game trying to add rockh4rd's ancient god sword and say
[code]add model 666[/code]
above it it would say
[code]could not find model 666[/code]
THANK YOU
